In 2004 Sam started experimenting with Flash ActionScript 2.0. The world would never be the same. Through his unique combination of insight, style, analytics, and brevity he has crafted app after app of inspiring code. Industry leaders pay close attention to what Sam is working on, as it is usually the next big breakthrough in web development technologies. He has crafted databases, styled sheets, and recursed functions. Bobby Flay said that Sam's eggs benedict is the best he has ever tasted, with the creamiest and most unbroken hollandaise sauce he'd ever even heard of. The future is the past, and technology becomes magic when you are working with Sam Darbonne. 